734
00:54:22,875 --> 00:54:25,915
VAN MEEGEREN: De Milo, with my
instructions, has made you a dress.

735
00:54:26,250 --> 00:54:29,665
It's a copy in every detail,
of the one worn by Madame Van Ees,

736
00:54:29,750 --> 00:54:32,415
in both The Concert
