some dirty stories.

745
00:55:04,500 --> 00:55:07,374
Oh, what you would like?
I could tell you about

746
00:55:07,416 --> 00:55:10,790
what Venus did to the unicorn
in Beardsley's Under the Hill.

747
00:55:10,875 --> 00:55:14,207
- Milo...
